    "content": "<h1 id=\"poets-eras-and-cities\">Poets, Eras, and Cities<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#poets-eras-and-cities\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h1>\n<p>This section holds the structured data behind Chekameh. Browse poets by era, explore literary centers, or dig into specific poem collections.</p>\n<h2 id=\"whats-here\">What's Here<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#whats-here\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Eras</strong> — The six historical periods of Persian poetry</li>\n<li><strong>Poets</strong> — Biographical profiles and works</li>\n<li><strong>Cities</strong> — Literary centers across the Persian-speaking world</li>\n<li><strong>Poem Books</strong> — Collections and anthologies</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"eras\">Eras<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#eras\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h2>\n<!-- Structure placeholder - content to be added -->\n\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Era</th>\n<th>Period</th>\n<th>Status</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Samanid</td>\n<td>875–1000 CE</td>\n<td>Coming soon</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Ghaznavid</td>\n<td>1000–1150 CE</td>\n<td>Coming soon</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Seljuk</td>\n<td>1150–1300 CE</td>\n<td>Coming soon</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Ilkhanate</td>\n<td>1260–1370 CE</td>\n<td>Coming soon</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Timurid</td>\n<td>1370–1500 CE</td>\n<td>Coming soon</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Safavid</td>\n<td>1500–1736 CE</td>\n<td>Coming soon</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"poets\">Poets<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#poets\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h2>\n<!-- Structure placeholder - content to be added -->\n\n<p>Profiles for each poet will include:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Birth and death dates</li>\n<li>Key locations</li>\n<li>Major works</li>\n<li>Literary style and influences</li>\n<li>Connections to other poets</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"cities\">Cities<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#cities\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h2>\n<!-- Structure placeholder - content to be added -->\n\n<p>City entries will cover:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Historical names and modern equivalents</li>\n<li>Time periods of literary activity</li>\n<li>Notable poets associated with the city</li>\n<li>Geographic and cultural context</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"poem-books\">Poem Books<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#poem-books\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h2>\n<!-- Structure placeholder - content to be added -->\n\n<p>Information on major collections:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Shahnameh</li>\n<li>Masnavi</li>\n<li>Divan-e Hafez</li>\n<li>Bustan and Gulistan</li>\n<li>And more</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<p><em>Data is being added progressively. Check back for updates.</em></p>",
